      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit boasts a crisp throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The double-VANOS system has been recently overhauled to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to address the chassis's known fatigue points. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator for better thermal management. A mechanically sound example ready for the twisties.",
